text: The club house The stadium entrance Narukerä are a Finnish bandy club from Pori. Narukerä finished in 3rd position in the Bandyliiga in the 2005-2006 season and also competed in the Bandy World Cup. In 2012 they reached the final of Bandyliiga.Kampparit new Finnish Champions in bandy They have won it once in their history, in the 1998/1999 season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Bandy clubs in Finland Category:Bandy clubs established in 1965
